      <title>新管道为加拿大原油带来稳定期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/new-pipeline-ushers-in-period-of-stability-for-canadian-crude</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于扩建后的跨山输油管道的启动为该国的石油生产商提供了新的运输选择和更广泛的买家群体，加拿大重质原油的折扣达到了两年多以来最稳定的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/new-pipeline-ushers-in-period-of-stability-for-canadian-crude</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 15:47:22 GMT</pubDate>
